text: The 2016 Tulsa Golden Hurricane men's soccer team will represent the University of Tulsa during the 2016 NCAA Division I men's soccer season. It will be the program's 37th season.http://sidearm.sites.s3.amazonaws.com/tulsahurricane.com/documents/2016/8/5/TU_MSO16_MediaGuide_LR.pdf?id=10434 ==Before the season== ===Transfers out / departures=== Adrian Smart transferred to Bloomfield College. Jordan Speed transferred to Midwestern State. Geoffrey Dee transferred to Louisville. Aymar Sigue transferred to Penn State. Zach Jackson transferred to Furman. Tony Doellefeld transferred to Belmont.
